column5: Took the dog for a walk at noon today. At the end  of my driveway, the dog starts going berserk. I look up and look who stopped by for lunch!  I thought of you Brian!HH
Always cool when the critters stop by to visit Joe.  lol
Enough there for a full dinner, never mind lunch!!
I thought of you Brian!  HH  Yes, there is a resemblance isn't there.
That is cool…a few roast potatoes…awesome!
